<DIV>I think your actually getting the main point here (finally). Looking for a clear definitive way to progress my 24 man crew through content, with a story line to make it interesting. I really think it would be a win, win situation, if Someone could go through content like this, with an alternate, yet real line of progression. Of course after getting in the zone's, the zones themselve's wouldn't be changed. If we can get into Time (The weaker phase), then to get to Quarm we would have to do the same fights any other guild did to get through the phases to reach him. If my guild is unable to do that, then at least the&nbsp; member's that wish to do him, can indeed join a guild whose doing Time, and will be able to have the relevant flag's to join that guild (Those that have pre-requisits). </DIV>
